Project origin and non-affiliation
-----------------------------------
LocaQL is an independent, community-driven local development platform
for BigQuery-compatible workflows. Its scope was informed by, and its
early planning referenced, the open-source project `goccy/bigquery-emulator`
(MIT License) as an optional upstream source of inspiration — LocaQL does
not incorporate that project's source code and is not a source fork of it.

